Package: rigr 
Title: Type-aware, test-driven data transformation
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Peder", "Landsverk", email = "pglandsverk@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Write data transformation scripts with a YAML header that
   explicates assumptions about the raw data, and the result
   of the transformation. 
